#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&LabPlot; is a &kde; application for interactive graphing and analysis of "
"scientific data. &LabPlot; provides an easy way to create, manage and edit "
"plots."
msgstr ""
"&LabPlot; je &kde; aplikacija za interaktivno risanje grafov in analizo "
"znanstvenih podatkov. &LabPlot; omogoča enostaven način ustvarjanja, "
"upravljanja in urejanja grafikonov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "Features:"
msgstr "Zmožnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Project-based management of data"
msgstr "Projektno upravljanje podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Project-explorer for management and organization of created objects in "
"different folders and sub-folders"
msgstr ""
"Raziskovalec projektov za upravljanje in organizacijo ustvarjenih predmetov "
"v različnih mapah in podmapah"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Spreadsheet with basic functionality for manual data entry or for generation "
"of uniform and non-uniform random numbers"
msgstr ""
"Preglednica z osnovno funkcionalnostjo za ročni vnos podatkov ali za "
"generiranje enakomerno in neenakomerno porazdeljenih naključnih števil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Import of external ASCII-data into the project for further editing and "
"visualization"
msgstr ""
"Uvoz zunanjih ASCII-podatkov v projekt za nadaljnje urejanje in vizualizacijo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "Export of spreadsheet to an ASCII-file"
msgstr "Izvoz preglednice v datoteko ASCII"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Worksheet as the main parent object for plots, labels &etc;, supports "
"different layouts and zooming functions"
msgstr ""
"Delovni list kot glavni nadrejeni objekt za izrise, oznake &etc; podpira "
"različne postavitve in funkcije povečave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Export of worksheet to different formats (pdf, eps, png and svg)"
msgstr "Izvoz delovnega lista v različne formate (pdf, eps, png in svg)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Great variety of editing capabilities for properties of worksheet and its "
"objects"
msgstr ""
"Velika izbira možnosti urejanja lastnosti delovnega lista in njegovih "
"predmetov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cartesian plots, created either from imported or manually created data sets "
"or via mathematical equation"
msgstr ""
"Kartezični diagrami, ustvarjeni iz uvoženih ali ročno ustvarjenih nizov "
"podatkov ali prek matematične enačbe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Definition of mathematical formulas is supported by syntax-highlighting and "
"completion and by the list of thematicaly grouped mathematical and physical "
"constants and functions"
msgstr ""
"Definicija matematičnih formul je podprta z označevanjem in dopolnjevanjem "
"sintakse ter s seznamom tematsko razvrščenih matematičnih in fizikalnih "
"konstant in funkcij"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Investigation of plotted data is supported by many zooming and navigation "
"features"
msgstr ""
"Raziskovanje izrisanih podatkov je podprto s številnimi funkcijami povečave "
"in navigacije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Several analysis functions and methods for data reduction, differentiation, "
"integration, interpolation, smoothing, (nonlinear) fitting, Fourier filter "
"and Fourier transform"
msgstr ""
"Več analitičnih funkcij in metod za reduciranje podatkov, diferenciacijo, "
"integracijo, interpolacijo, glajenje, (nelinearno) prilagajanje, Fourierjev "
"filter in Fourierjevo transformacijo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Linear and non-linear fits to data, several fit-models are predefined and "
"custom models with arbitrary number of parameters can be provided"
msgstr ""
"Linearno in nelinearno prileganje podatkom, več modelov prileganja je "
"vnaprej določenih in na voljo je mogoče modele po meri s poljubnim številom "
"parametrov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "Supports many CAS backends like Maxima, Python, KAlgebra, Sage"
msgstr "Podpira številna zaledja CAS, kot so Maxima, Python, KAlgebra, Sage"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Nice Worksheet view for evaluating expressions"
msgstr "Lep pogled delovnega lista za vrednotenje izrazov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "Easy plugin based structure to add different Backends"
msgstr "Preprosta struktura na osnovi vtičnikov za dodajanje različnih zaledij"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Plugin based assistant dialogs for common tasks (like integrating a function "
"or entering a matrix)"
msgstr ""
"Pogovorna okna pomočnika, ki temeljijo na vtičnikih, za običajna opravila "
"(kot je integracija funkcije ali vnos matrike)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Datapicker for manual or (semi-)automatic data extraction from imported "
"images containing plots and curves."
msgstr ""
"Izvlečnik podatkov za ročno ali (pol)samodejno ekstrakcijo podatkov iz "
"uvoženih slik, ki vsebujejo diagrame in krivulje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&LabPlot; can be found on its homepage at kde.org: <ulink url=\"https://"
"labplot.kde.org/\">https://labplot.kde.org/</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&LabPlot; najdete na njegovi domači strani na kde.org: <ulink url=\"https://"
"labplot.kde.org/\">https://labplot.kde.org/</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &LabPlot;"
msgstr "Uporaba &LabPlot;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interface Overview"
msgstr "Pregled vmesnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&LabPlot; follows the MDI (Multiple Document Interface) philosophy - all the "
"created application objects are placed as sub-windows in the <link linkend="
"\"main-area\">Main Area</link> of the application window. The <link linkend="
"\"project-explorer\">Project Explorer</link> serves as the tool to create "
"and organize those objects in a tree-like structure. The <link linkend="
"\"properties-explorer\">Properties Explorer</link> is used to modify the "
"properties of the currently selected object(s). Many functions are reachable "
"via the main menu and via object specific toolbars and context menus. "
"Additional information and application notifications are shown in the status "
"bar."
msgstr ""
"&LabPlot; sledi filozofiji MDI (Multiple Document Interface) - vsi "
"ustvarjeni objekti aplikacije so postavljeni kot podokna v <link linkend="
"\"main-area\">Glavno področje</link> okna aplikacije. <link linkend="
"\"project-explorer\">Project Explorer</link> služi kot orodje za ustvarjanje "
"in organiziranje teh predmetov v drevesni strukturi. <link linkend="
"\"properties-explorer\">Raziskovalec lastnosti</link> se uporablja za "
"spreminjanje lastnosti trenutno izbranih predmetov. Številne funkcije so "
"dosegljive prek glavnega menija in prek orodnih vrstic za posamezne predmete "
"in kontekstnih menijev. Dodatne informacije in obvestila o aplikaciji so "
"prikazani v vrstici stanja."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "The default &LabPlot; window"
msgstr "Privzeto &LabPlot; okno"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "Project Explorer"
msgstr "Raziskovalec projektov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Project Explorer is the main part of &LabPlot; aimed to handle its "
"objects. Objects are organized in a tree-like structure representing the "
"parent-child relations between the different objects. Folders and sub-"
"folders can introduce additional grouping for the different objects."
msgstr ""
"Raziskovalec projektov je glavni del &LabPlot; namenjen ravnanju s svojimi "
"predmeti. Predmeti so organizirani v drevesni strukturi, ki predstavlja "
"odnose med staršem in otrokom med različnimi predmeti. Mape in podmape lahko "
"uvedejo dodatno združevanje za različne predmete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Project explorer is a dockable window and can be placed at an arbitrary "
"place. The user can determine which columns should be shown by selecting/"
"deselecting the columns of interest in the context menu (&RMB; click on an "
"empty place in the tree-view or its header). Furthermore, the list of shown "
"objects can be reduced by providing a filter in the <guilabel>Search/Filter</"
"guilabel> text field."
msgstr ""
"Raziskovalec projektov je okno, ki ga je mogoče priklopiti in ga lahko "
"postavite na poljubno mesto. Uporabnik lahko določi, kateri stolpci naj bodo "
"prikazani, tako da v kontekstnem meniju izbere/prekliče izbor stolpcev, ki "
"ga zanimajo (&RMB; kliknite na prazno mesto v drevesnem pogledu ali njegovi "
"glavi). Poleg tega lahko seznam prikazanih predmetov skrajšate tako, da "
"zagotovite filter v besedilnem polju <guilabel>Iskanje/Filter</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main Area"
msgstr "Glavno območje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Created objects having a view (like worksheet, spreadsheet &etc;) are placed "
"in the main area of the application. Depending on the current setting for "
"the user interface, windows are placed either as independent and freely "
"moveable sub-windows (interface \"Sub-window view\") or as tabs in a tabbed "
"view (interface \"Tabbed view\")."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarjeni predmeti s pogledom (kot so delovni list, preglednica &etc;) so "
"postavljeni v glavno področje aplikacije. Odvisno od trenutne nastavitve "
"uporabniškega vmesnika so okna postavljena bodisi kot neodvisna in prosto "
"premikajoča se podokna (vmesnik \"Pogled pod oknom\") ali kot zavihki v "
"pogledu z zavihki (vmesnik \"Pogled z zavihki\")."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When sub-windows are used, all windows of objects belonging to the currently "
"selected folder only are shown. Alternatively, the visibility of windows can "
"be extended to the currently selected folder and its sub-folders or to all "
"windows in the project. This behaviour is controlled via the parameter "
"\"Window visibility policy\" accessible via the context menu of the project "
"explorer."
msgstr ""
"Ko se uporabljajo podokna, se prikažejo vsa okna objektov, ki pripadajo samo "
"trenutno izbrani mapi. Druga možnost je, da se vidnost oken razširi na "
"trenutno izbrano mapo in njene podmape ali na vsa okna v projektu. To "
"vedenje je nadzorovano s parametrom \"Politika vidnosti oken\", ki je "
"dostopen prek kontekstnega menija raziskovalca projektov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "Properties Explorer"
msgstr "Raziskovalec lastnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Properties explorer allows the user to modify the currently selected object "
"in the project explorer. A great variety of object properties can be edited "
"in undoable/redoable way. Editing of multiple objects of the same time is "
"also possible."
msgstr ""
"Raziskovalec lastnosti omogoča uporabniku, da spremeni trenutno izbrani "
"predmet v raziskovalcu projektov. Veliko različnih lastnosti predmetov je "
"mogoče urejati na način, ki ga je mogoče razveljaviti/ponoviti. Možno je "
"tudi urejanje več objektov hkrati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Properties explorer is a dockable window and can be placed at an arbitrary "
"place."
msgstr ""
"Raziskovalec lastnosti je okno, ki ga je mogoče priklopiti in ga lahko "
"postavite na poljubno mesto."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spreadsheet"
msgstr "Preglednica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The spreadsheet is the main part of &LabPlot; when working with data and "
"consists of columns. Column is the basic data set in &LabPlot; used for "
"plotting and data analysis. Every column of the spreadsheet is specified by "
"its name and the type - numeric, text, month names, day names and date and "
"time. Also, for each type different representation formats can be assigned "
"like decimal or scientific format for numeric columns &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Preglednica je glavni del &LabPlot; pri delu s podatki in je sestavljen iz "
"stolpcev. Stolpec je osnovni nabor podatkov v &LabPlot; uporablja se za "
"risanje in analizo podatkov. Vsak stolpec preglednice je določen z imenom in "
"vrsto - številsko, besedilno, imena mesecev, imena dni ter datum in čas. "
"Prav tako je za vsako vrsto mogoče dodeliti različne predstavitvene oblike, "
"kot je decimalna ali znanstvena oblika za številske stolpce &etc;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can mask selected data points in the spreadsheet "
"(<menuchoice><guimenu>Selection</guimenu><guimenuitem>Mask Selection</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the spreadsheet cell context menu). Masked "
"data is not plotted and is also excluded from data analysis functions like "
"fitting &etc; Alternatively, you can mask or drop values in a column "
"(<menuchoice><guimenu>Mask Values</guimenu></menuchoice> or "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Drop Values</guimenu></menuchoice> from the column "
"context menu) by specifying a range. When specifying which values to mask or "
"to drop, several operators (“equal to”, “greater than”, “lesser than”, "
"&etc;) are available. These operations can help to hide or to remove some "
"outliers in the data set prior to, &eg;, performing a fit to this data set."
msgstr ""
"Izbrane podatkovne točke v preglednici lahko maskirate "
"(<menuchoice><guimenu>Izbor</guimenu><guimenuitem>Maskiraj izbor</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> v kontekstnem meniju celice preglednice). "
"Zamaskirani podatki niso narisani in so tudi izključeni iz funkcij analize "
"podatkov, kot je prileganje &etc;. Lahko pa tudi maskirate ali spustite "
"vrednosti v stolpcu (<menuchoice><guimenu>Maskiraj vrednosti</guimenu></"
"menuchoice> ali <menuchoice><guimenu>Izpusti vrednosti</guimenu></"
"menuchoice> iz kontekstnega menija stolpca ) z navedbo obsega. Pri "
"določanju, katere vrednosti naj se prikrijejo ali izpustijo, je na voljo več "
"operatorjev (»enako«, »večje od«, »manjše od« &etc;). Te operacije lahko "
"pomagajo skriti ali odstraniti nekatere izstopajoče vrednosti v naboru "
"podatkov, preden &eg; izvedete prilagajanje temu naboru podatkov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Any spreadsheet function can be reached via the context menu (&RMB; click). "
"You can cut, copy and paste between spreadsheets, generate, normalize and "
"sort data and finally make plots out of your data."
msgstr ""
"Do katere koli funkcije preglednice lahko pridete prek kontekstnega menija "
"(&RMB; klik). Lahko izrezujete, kopirate in lepite med preglednicami, "
"ustvarjate, normalizirate in razvrščate podatke ter na koncu iz svojih "
"podatkov naredite grafikone."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"New data can be produced either by entering it manually in the spreadsheet "
"or by generating the data according to a certain prescription. &LabPlot; "
"provides 5 different methods to generate data, accessible via the context "
"menu of the column:"
msgstr ""
"Nove podatke lahko proizvedemo z ročnim vnosom v preglednico ali z "
"generiranjem podatkov po določenem receptu. &LabPlot; ponuja 5 različnih "
"metod za ustvarjanje podatkov, dostopnih prek kontekstnega menija stolpca:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Row Numbers - values in the column are set according to its row number, this "
"provide an easy way to quickly create an index."
msgstr ""
"Številke vrstic – vrednosti v stolpcu so nastavljene glede na številko "
"vrstice, kar omogoča preprost način za hitro ustvarjanje indeksa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Const Values - values in the column are set to a constant value provided by "
"the user."
msgstr ""
"Konstantne vrednosti – vrednosti v stolpcu so nastavljene na konstantno "
"vrednost, ki jo poda uporabnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Equidistant values (for numeric columns only) - given the minimal and the "
"maximal values, the equidistant values can be either generated by fixing the "
"total number of values in that range or by fixing the increment (distance)."
msgstr ""
"Ekvidistančne vrednosti (samo za številske stolpce) – glede na najmanjšo in "
"največjo vrednost je mogoče ekvidistančne vrednosti generirati s fiksiranjem "
"skupnega števila vrednosti v tem obsegu ali s fiksiranjem prirastka "
"(razdalje)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Random values (for numeric columns only) - values are randomly generated "
"according to the selected distribution. To generate uniformly distributed "
"random numbers, select \"Flat\" distribution."
msgstr ""
"Naključne vrednosti (samo za številske stolpce) - vrednosti so naključno "
"generirane glede na izbrano porazdelitev. Če želite ustvariti enakomerno "
"porazdeljena naključna števila, izberite porazdelitev \"Enakomerna\"."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the simplest cases a non-uniform distribution is calculated analytically "
"from the uniform distribution of a random number generator by applying an "
"appropriate transformation. More complicated distributions are created by "
"the acceptance-rejection method, which compares the desired distribution "
"against a distribution which is similar and known analytically."
msgstr ""
"V najpreprostejših primerih se neenakomerna porazdelitev izračuna analitično "
"iz enakomerne porazdelitve generatorja naključnih števil z uporabo ustrezne "
"transformacije. Bolj zapletene porazdelitve se ustvarijo z metodo sprejema-"
"zavrnitve, ki primerja želeno porazdelitev s podobno in analitično znano "
"porazdelitvijo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Function values (for numeric columns only) - values are generated according "
"to a mathematical function provided by the user, a column (data set) "
"containing the function arguments has to be provided. It is possible to "
"define a multivariant function and to provide a data set (a column in a "
"spreadsheet) for each of the variables. The corresponding dialog supports "
"the creation of arbitrary number of variables."
msgstr ""
"Funkcijske vrednosti (samo za številske stolpce) – vrednosti se generirajo v "
"skladu z matematično funkcijo, ki jo poda uporabnik, zagotoviti je treba "
"stolpec (nabor podatkov), ki vsebuje argumente funkcije. Možno je definirati "
"multivariantno funkcijo in zagotoviti nabor podatkov (stolpec v preglednici) "
"za vsako od spremenljivk. Ustrezno pogovorno okno podpira ustvarjanje "
"poljubnega števila spremenljivk."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Already existing data can be imported into a spreadsheet from external files "
"via the <link linkend=\"importdialog\">\"Import Data\" dialog</link>. "
"Imported data will be stored in the project file. Changes on data, performed "
"either in the spreadsheet or in the external file after the import, are not "
"synchronized anymore."
msgstr ""
"Že obstoječe podatke je mogoče uvoziti v preglednico iz zunanjih datotek "
"prek <link linkend=\"importdialog\">pogovornega okna »Uvoz podatkov«</link>. "
"Uvoženi podatki bodo shranjeni v projektni datoteki. Spremembe podatkov, "
"opravljene bodisi v preglednici bodisi v zunanji datoteki po uvozu, se ne "
"sinhronizirajo več."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The data in the spreadsheet can be exported to an external file (see <link "
"linkend=\"exportdialog\">Export Dialog</link>)."
msgstr ""
"Podatke v preglednici je mogoče izvoziti v zunanjo datoteko (glejte <link "
"linkend=\"exportdialog\">Pogovorno okno za izvoz</link>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid "Matrix"
msgstr "Matrix"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:287
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Matrix is another container for matrix-like data. This container is "
"presented like a table or, alternatively, as a two-dimensional greyscale "
"image. The elements of such a table/matrix can be thought as being the Z-"
"values, Z=Z(X,Y), with X and Y values being the row and column numbers, "
"respectively. The transition from the row and column numbers to the logical "
"coordinates is done via an explicit user-defined mapping of both "
"representations."
msgstr ""
"Matrix je še en vsebnik za podatke, podobne matriki. Ta vsebnik je "
"predstavljen kot tabela ali, alternativno, kot dvodimenzionalna slika v "
"sivinah. Elemente takšne tabele/matrike lahko obravnavamo kot Z-vrednosti, "
"Z=Z(X,Y), pri čemer sta vrednosti X in Y številki vrstic oziroma stolpcev. "
"Prehod s številk vrstic in stolpcev na logične koordinate se izvede preko "
"eksplicitne uporabniško definirane preslikave obeh predstavitev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The matrix data can either be entered manually or via an import from an "
"external file. Similar to the data generation for a column in a spreadsheet, "
"the matrix can be filled with constant values or via a formula, too. The "
"screenshot below shows the image view of a matrix together with the formula "
"that was used to generate the matrix elements:"
msgstr ""
"Podatke o matriki je mogoče vnesti ročno ali z uvozom iz zunanje datoteke. "
"Podobno kot pri generiranju podatkov za stolpec v preglednici lahko matriko "
"polnimo s konstantnimi vrednostmi ali tudi s formulo. Spodnji posnetek "
"zaslona prikazuje slikovni pogled matrike skupaj s formulo, ki je bila "
"uporabljena za ustvarjanje elementov matrike:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "Workbook"
msgstr "Delovni zvezek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Workbook helps the user to better organize and to group different data "
"containers (Spreadsheet and Matrix). This object serves as the parent "
"container for multiple Spreadsheet- and/or Matrix-objects and puts them "
"together in a view with multiple tabs:"
msgstr ""
"Delovni zvezek uporabniku pomaga bolje organizirati in združevati različne "
"vsebnike podatkov (preglednico in matriko). Ta objekt služi kot nadrejeni "
"vsebnik za več predmetov preglednice in/ali matrike in jih združi v pogled z "
"več zavihki:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With folders it is already possible to bring some structure in the <link "
"linkend=\"project-explorer\">Project Explorer</link> and to group together "
"several related objects (spreadsheets with data stemming from text files of "
"similar origin, red, green and blue values of an image imported into three "
"different matrices, &etc;). With Workbook the user has the possibility for "
"another additional grouping."
msgstr ""
"Z mapami je že mogoče prinesti nekaj strukture v <link linkend=\"project-"
"explorer\">Project Explorer</link> in združiti več povezanih predmetov "
"(preglednice s podatki, ki izvirajo iz besedilnih datotek podobnega izvora, "
"rdeče, zelene in modre vrednosti slike, uvožene v tri različne matrike, "
"&etc;). Z delovnim zvezkom ima uporabnik možnost še enega dodatnega "
"grupiranja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "Worksheet"
msgstr "Delovni list"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The worksheet is, besides the data containers <link linkend=\"spreadsheet"
"\">Spreadsheet</link> and <link linkend=\"matrix\">Matrix</link>, another "
"central part of the application and provides an area for showing and "
"grouping together different kinds of worksheet objects - plots, labels &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Delovni list je poleg podatkovnih vsebnikov <link linkend=\"spreadsheet"
"\">Preglednica</link> in <link linkend=\"matrix\">Matrix</link> še en "
"osrednji del aplikacije in ponuja območje za prikaz in združevanje skupaj "
"različne vrste predmetov delovnega lista - risbe, oznake &etc;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Worksheets can either have a fixed size (a user defined size or one of the "
"predefined sizes like A4, Letter &etc;) or they can fill out the complete "
"available area for the worksheet window. Multiple plots can be arranged on "
"the worksheet in a vertical, horizontal or grid layouts."
msgstr ""
"Delovni listi imajo lahko fiksno velikost (uporabniško določena velikost ali "
"ena od vnaprej določenih velikosti, kot je A4, Letter &etc;) ali pa lahko "
"zapolnijo celotno razpoložljivo območje za okno delovnega lista. Na delovnem "
"listu je mogoče razporediti več risb v navpični, vodoravni ali mrežni "
"postavitvi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many properties of the worksheet like size, background colour and layout "
"settings can be changed in the \"Worksheet properties\" pane."
msgstr ""
"Številne lastnosti delovnega lista, kot so velikost, barva ozadja in "
"nastavitve postavitve, lahko spremenite v podoknu »Lastnosti delovnega "
"lista«."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:344
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Different worksheet actions dealing with the creation of new objects, "
"changing of the current mouse mode or zooming can be accessed via the "
"toolbar, main menu or the context menu of the worksheet in the <link linkend="
"\"project-explorer\">project explorer</link>."
msgstr ""
"Do različnih dejanj delovnega lista, ki se ukvarjajo z ustvarjanjem novih "
"predmetov, spreminjanjem trenutnega načina miške ali povečavo, lahko "
"dostopate prek orodne vrstice, glavnega menija ali kontekstnega menija "
"delovnega lista v <link linkend=\"project-explorer\">raziskovalcu projektov</"
"link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The results shown on the worksheet can be exported to different formats via "
"the <link linkend=\"exportdialog\">export dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Rezultate, prikazane na delovnem listu, je mogoče izvoziti v različne "
"formate prek <link linkend=\"exportdialog\">pogovornega okna za izvoz</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid "CAS Worksheet"
msgstr "CAS delovni list"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The CAS worksheet is, besides the <link linkend=\"worksheet\">worksheet</"
"link>, the third central part of the application and provides an area to you "
"use your favorite mathematical applications from within an elegant Worksheet "
"Interface."
msgstr ""
"Delovni list CAS je poleg <link linkend=\"worksheet\">delovnega lista</link> "
"tretji osrednji del aplikacije in nudi področje, kjer lahko uporabljate "
"svoje najljubše matematične aplikacije znotraj elegantnega vmesnika "
"delovnega lista."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&LabPlot; offers you several choices for the backends you wish to use with "
"it. The choice to make depends on what you want to achieve."
msgstr ""
"&LabPlot; vam ponuja več možnosti za zaledja, ki jih želite uporabiti z "
"njim. Izbira je odvisna od tega, kaj želite doseči."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid "Currently the following backends are available:"
msgstr "Trenutno so na voljo naslednja zaledja:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sage:"
msgstr "Sage:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:372
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sage is a free open-source mathematics software system licensed under the "
"GPL. It combines the power of many existing open-source packages, within a "
"common Python-based interface. See <ulink url=\"http://sagemath.org\">http://"
"sagemath.org</ulink> for more information."
msgstr ""
"Sage je prosti odprtokodni matematični programski sistem z licenco GPL. "
"Združuje moč številnih obstoječih odprtokodnih paketov v skupnem vmesniku, "
"ki temelji na Pythonu. Za več informacij glejte <ulink url=\"http://sagemath."
"org\">http://sagemath.org</ulink>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:380
#, no-c-format
msgid "Maxima:"
msgstr "Maxima:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Maxima is a system for the manipulation of symbolic and numeric expressions, "
"including differentiation, integration, Taylor series, Laplace transforms, "
"ordinary differential equations, systems of linear equations, polynomials, "
"sets, lists, vectors, matrices, and tensors. Maxima yields high-precision "
"numeric results by using exact fractions, arbitrary precision integers, and "
"variable precision floating point numbers. Maxima can plot functions and "
"data in two and three dimensions. See <ulink url=\"http://maxima.sourceforge."
"net\">http://maxima.sourceforge.net</ulink> for more information."
msgstr ""
"Maxima je sistem za manipulacijo simbolnih in numeričnih izrazov, vključno z "
"diferenciacijo, integracijo, Taylorjevo vrsto, Laplaceovo transformacijo, "
"navadnimi diferencialnimi enačbami, sistemi linearnih enačb, polinomi, "
"množicami, seznami, vektorji, matricami in tenzorji. Maxima daje visoko "
"natančne numerične rezultate z uporabo natančnih ulomkov, poljubno natančnih "
"celih števil in števil s plavajočo vejico s spremenljivo natančnostjo. "
"Maxima lahko izriše funkcije in podatke v dveh in treh dimenzijah. Za več "
"informacij glejte <ulink url=\"http://maxima.sourceforge.net\">http://maxima."
"sourceforge.net</ulink>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>R:</term>"
msgstr "<term>R:</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"R is a language and environment for statistical computing and graphics, "
"similar to the S language and environment. It provides a wide variety of "
"statistical (linear and nonlinear modelling, classical statistical tests, "
"time-series analysis, classification, clustering, ...) and graphical "
"techniques, and is highly extensible. The S language is often the vehicle of "
"choice for research in statistical methodology, and R provides an open-"
"source route to this. See <ulink url=\"http://www.r-project.org\">http://www."
"r-project.org</ulink> for more information."
msgstr ""
"R je jezik in okolje za statistično računalništvo in grafiko, podobno jeziku "
"in okolju S. Omogoča široko paleto statističnih (linearno in nelinearno "
"modeliranje, klasični statistični testi, analiza časovnih vrst, "
"klasifikacija, združevanje v gruče, ...) in grafičnih tehnik ter je zelo "
"razširljiv. Jezik S je pogosto izbrano sredstvo za raziskave v statistični "
"metodologiji, R pa ponuja odprtokodno pot do tega. Za več informacij glejte "
"<ulink url=\"http://www.r-project.org\">http://www.r-project.org</ulink>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:408
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kalgebra;:"
msgstr "&kalgebra;:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kalgebra; is a MathML-based graph calculator, that ships with &kde; "
"Education project. See <ulink url=\"http://edu.kde.org/kalgebra/\">http://"
"edu.kde.org/kalgebra/</ulink> for more information."
msgstr ""
"&kalgebra; je grafični kalkulator, ki temelji na MathML in je priložen &kde; "
"Izobraževalni projekt. Glejte <ulink url=\"http://edu.kde.org/kalgebra/"
"\">http://edu.kde.org/kalgebra/</ulink> za več informacij."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:417
#, no-c-format
msgid "Qalculate!:"
msgstr "Qalculate!:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:419
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Qalculate! is not your regular software replication of the cheapest "
"available calculator. Qalculate! aims to make full use of the superior "
"interface, power and flexibility of modern computers. The center of "
"attention in Qalculate! is the expression entry. Instead of entering each "
"number in a mathematical expression separately, you can directly write the "
"whole expression and later modify it. The interpretation of expressions is "
"flexible and fault tolerant, and if you nevertheless do something wrong, "
"Qalculate! will tell you so. Not fully solvable expressions are however not "
"errors. Qalculate! will simplify as far as it can and answer with an "
"expression. In addition to numbers and arithmetic operators, an expression "
"may contain any combination of variables, units, and functions. See <ulink "
"url=\"http://qalculate.sourceforge.net/\">http://qalculate.sourceforge.net/</"
"ulink> for more information."
msgstr ""
"Qalculate! ni vaša redna programska replikacija najcenejšega razpoložljivega "
"kalkulatorja. Qalculate! želi v celoti izkoristiti vrhunski vmesnik, moč in "
"prilagodljivost sodobnih računalnikov. V središču pozornosti v Qalculate! je "
"vnos izraza. Namesto da bi vsako število v matematični izraz vnesli posebej, "
"lahko neposredno napišete celoten izraz in ga pozneje spremenite. Razlaga "
"izrazov je prilagodljiva in tolerantna na napake, in če kljub temu naredite "
"kaj narobe, bo Qalculate! to povedal. Nerešljivi izrazi pa niso napake. "
"Qalculate! bo poenostavil, kolikor lahko, in odgovoril z izrazom. Poleg "
"števil in aritmetičnih operatorjev lahko izraz vsebuje poljubno kombinacijo "
"spremenljivk, enot in funkcij. Za več informacij glejte <ulink url=\"http://"
"qalculate.sourceforge.net/\">http://qalculate.sourceforge.net/</ulink>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:436
#, no-c-format
msgid "Python2:"
msgstr "Python2:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:438
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Python is a remarkably powerful dynamic programming language that is used in "
"a wide variety of application domains. There are several Python packages to "
"scientific programming."
msgstr ""
"Python je izjemno zmogljiv dinamični programski jezik, ki se uporablja v "
"najrazličnejših aplikacijskih domenah. Obstaja več paketov Python za "
"znanstveno programiranje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:443
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Python is distributed under Python Software Foundation license (GPL "
"compatible). See the <ulink url=\"http://www.python.org/\">official website</"
"ulink> for more information."
msgstr ""
"Python se distribuira pod licenco Python Software Foundation (združljivo z "
"GPL). Za več informacij obiščite <ulink url=\"http://www.python.org/"
"\">uradno spletno stran</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This backend adds an additional item to the &cantor;'s main menu, "
"<guimenu>Package</guimenu>. The only item of this menu is "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Package</guimenu><guimenuitem>Import Package</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This item can be used to import Python packages "
"to the worksheet."
msgstr ""
"To zaledje doda dodaten element v glavni meni &cantor;, <guimenu>Paket</"
"guimenu>. Edini element v tem meniju je <menuchoice><guimenu>Paket</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Uvozi paket</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Ta element "
"lahko uporabite za uvoz paketov Python na delovni list."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:452
#, no-c-format
msgid "This backend supports Python 2 only."
msgstr "To zaledje podpira samo Python 2."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:459
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scilab:"
msgstr "Scilab:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:461
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scilab is an free software, cross-platform numerical computational package "
"and a high-level, numerically oriented programming language."
msgstr ""
"Scilab je prosta programska oprema, večplatformni numerični računski paket "
"in visokonivojski numerično usmerjen programski jezik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scilab is distributed under CeCILL license (GPL compatible). See <ulink url="
"\"http://www.scilab.org/\">http://www.scilab.org/</ulink> for more "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Scilab se distribuira pod licenco CeCILL (združljivo z GPL). Za več "
"informacij glejte <ulink url=\"http://www.scilab.org/\">http://www.scilab."
"org/</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:469
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You need Scilab version 5.5 or higher to be installed in your system to make "
"this backend usable."
msgstr ""
"Za uporabo tega zaledja morate v sistem namestiti Scilab različice 5.5 ali "
"novejšo."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:476
#, no-c-format
msgid "Octave:"
msgstr "Octave:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:478
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&GNU; Octave is a high-level language, primarily intended for numerical "
"computations. It provides a convenient command line interface for solving "
"linear and nonlinear problems numerically, and for performing other "
"numerical experiments using a language that is mostly compatible with <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.mathworks.com/products/matlab/\">MATLAB</ulink>. See <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.gnu.org/software/octave/\">http://www.gnu.org/software/"
"octave/</ulink> for more information."
msgstr ""
"&GNU; Octave je jezik visoke ravni, namenjen predvsem numeričnim izračunom. "
"Ponuja priročen vmesnik ukazne vrstice za numerično reševanje linearnih in "
"nelinearnih problemov ter za izvajanje drugih numeričnih poskusov z uporabo "
"jezika, ki je večinoma združljiv z <ulink url=\"http://www.mathworks.com/"
"products/matlab/\"> MATLAB</ulink>. Za več informacij glejte <ulink url="
"\"http://www.gnu.org/software/octave/\">http://www.gnu.org/software/octave/</"
"ulink>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:488
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lua:"
msgstr "Lua:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:490
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lua is a fast and lightweight scripting language, with a simple procedural "
"syntax. There are several libraries in Lua aimed at math and science."
msgstr ""
"Lua je hiter in lahek skriptni jezik s preprosto proceduralno sintakso. V "
"Lui je več knjižnic, namenjenih matematiki in naravoslovju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:493
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See <ulink url=\"http://www.lua.org/\">http://www.lua.org/</ulink> for more "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij glejte <ulink url=\"http://www.lua.org/\">http://www.lua."
"org/</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This backend supports <ulink url=\"http://luajit.org/\">luajit 2</ulink>."
msgstr "To zaledje podpira <ulink url=\"http://luajit.org/\">luajit 2</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:507
#, no-c-format
msgid "File Data Source"
msgstr "Datotečni vir podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:508
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A file data source is very similar in spirit to a spreadsheet with imported "
"data from an external file. The difference is that the imported data cannot "
"be shown and edited in &LabPlot; after the import anymore. This can be "
"sufficient &eg; if you only want to plot the data stemming from a "
"calculation in an external program (and exported to an ASCII-file "
"afterwards)."
msgstr ""
"Datotečni vir podatkov je po duhu zelo podoben preglednici z uvoženimi "
"podatki iz zunanje datoteke. Razlika je v tem, da uvoženih podatkov ni "
"mogoče prikazati in urejati v &LabPlot; po uvozu več. To lahko zadostuje, "
"&eg; če želite samo narisati podatke, ki izhajajo iz izračuna v zunanjem "
"programu (in jih nato izvoziti v datoteko ASCII)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:511
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Since no spreadsheet has to be filled with the imported data, the import "
"into a file data source is faster than into a spreadsheet which can be "
"advantageously when dealing with big files."
msgstr ""
"Ker nobene preglednice ni treba napolniti z uvoženimi podatki, je uvoz v "
"datotečni vir podatkov hitrejši kot v preglednico, kar je lahko prednost pri "
"delu z velikimi datotekami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to store the link to the external file in the project file "
"only and not its content. Each time the project file is opened in &LabPlot;, "
"the content is read from the external file again. Also, it is possible to "
"let &LabPlot; watch the file for changes - the content of the file data "
"source is updated if the external file was changed."
msgstr ""
"V projektno datoteko je mogoče shraniti samo povezavo do zunanje datoteke in "
"ne njene vsebine. Vsakič, ko se projektna datoteka odpre v &LabPlot;, se "
"vsebina znova prebere iz zunanje datoteke. Prav tako je mogoče pustiti, da "
"&LabPlot; spremlja datoteko za spremembe - vsebina vira podatkov datoteke se "
"posodobi, če je bila zunanja datoteka spremenjena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:522
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The additional options determining the import of the data are equivalent to "
"those provided in <link linkend=\"importdialog\">Import Dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Dodatne možnosti, ki določajo uvoz podatkov, so enakovredne tistim v <link "
"linkend=\"importdialog\">Pogovornem oknu za uvoz</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:529
#, no-c-format
msgid "Datapicker"
msgstr "Datapicker - izvlečnik podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:530
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Datapicker is a tool that allows you to easily extract data from image "
"files. The process of extraction consists mainly out of the following steps:"
msgstr ""
"Izvlečnik je orodje, ki vam omogoča enostavno pridobivanje podatkov iz "
"slikovnih datotek. Postopek ekstrakcije je sestavljen predvsem iz naslednjih "
"korakov:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:533
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Import an image containing plots and curves where you want to read the data "
"points from."
msgstr ""
"Uvozite sliko, ki vsebuje grafikone in krivulje, iz katerih želite prebrati "
"podatkovne točke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:534
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select the plot type (cartesian, polar, &etc;)."
msgstr "Izberite vrsto izrisa (kartezijsko, polarno, &etc;)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:535
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select tree reference points and provide values for them. With the help of "
"these points the logical coordinate system is determined."
msgstr ""
"Izberite referenčne točke drevesa in navedite vrednosti zanje. S pomočjo teh "
"točk se določi logični koordinatni sistem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:536
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a new datapicker curve and set the type of the error bars."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite novo krivuljo izvlečnika podatkov in nastavite vrsto vrstic napak."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:537
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch to the mouse mode \"Set Curve Points\" and start selecting points on "
"the imported image - the coordinates for the selected points are determined "
"and added to the spreadsheet \"Data\"."
msgstr ""
"Preklopite v način miške \"Nastavi točke krivulje\" in začnite izbirati "
"točke na uvoženi sliki - koordinate za izbrane točke so določene in dodane v "
"preglednico \"Podatki\"."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to add more then one datapicker curve. This is useful in case "
"the imported image contains several curves that need to be digitized. The "
"datapicker curve that is currently being selected in the <link linkend="
"\"project-explorer\">Project Explorer </link> is the \"active\" one - points "
"clicked on the datapicker image will be calculated and added to its data "
"spreadsheet."
msgstr ""
"Dodati je mogoče več kot eno krivuljo izvlečnika podatkov. To je uporabno, "
"če uvožena slika vsebuje več krivulj, ki jih je treba digitalizirati. "
"Krivulja izvlečnika podatkov, ki je trenutno izbrana v <link linkend="
"\"project-explorer\">Raziskovalcu projektov </link>, je \"aktivna\" - točke, "
"ki jih kliknete na sliki izvlečnika podatkov, bodo izračunane in dodane v "
"njegovo podatkovno preglednico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:549
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Calculated values are stored in different columns in data spreadsheets in "
"the datapicker. These columns behave exactly the same like other columns in "
"usual spreadsheets and can be directly used as source columns for curves in "
"your own plots."
msgstr ""
"Izračunane vrednosti so shranjene v različnih stolpcih podatkovnih "
"preglednic v izvlečniku podatkov. Ti stolpci se obnašajo popolnoma enako kot "
"drugi stolpci v običajnih preglednicah in jih je mogoče neposredno uporabiti "
"kot izvorne stolpce za krivulje v vaših lastnih izrisih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:554
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Datapicker supports the process of the data extraction with several helpers. "
"To place the points more precisely, a magnification glass with different "
"magnification levels is available. Also, the last selected point can be "
"shifted with the help of the navigation keys. Furthermore, when reading data "
"points having error bars, datapicker automatically creates bars indicating "
"the end points of the error bars. Those bars can be pulled with the mouse "
"until the required length (the distance to the data point) is reached."
msgstr ""
"Izvlečnik podatkov podpira postopek pridobivanja podatkov z več pomočniki. "
"Za natančnejšo postavitev točk je na voljo povečevalno steklo z različnimi "
"stopnjami povečave. Prav tako lahko zadnjo izbrano točko premaknete s "
"pomočjo navigacijskih tipk. Poleg tega pri branju podatkovnih točk z "
"vrsticami napak izvlečnik podatkov samodejno ustvari vrstice, ki označujejo "
"končne točke vrstic napak. Te palice lahko vlečete z miško, dokler ni "
"dosežena zahtevana dolžina (razdalja do podatkovne točke)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:562
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The procedure for the extraction of data from an imported plot as described "
"above is feasible when dealing with a limited number of points. In case the "
"curves in the imported image are given as solid lines, the datapicker tool "
"in &LabPlot; allows to read them (semi-)automatically. For this, after a new "
"datapicker curve was added as described above, switch to the mouse mode "
"\"Select Curve Segments\". The curves on the plot are recognized and "
"highlighted. By clicking on a highlighted curve (or one of its segments), "
"points along this curve are created. The length of a segment and the density "
"of created points (separation between two points) are adjustable parameters. "
"On the screenshots below, after switching to the segment mode all black "
"lines were highlighted (green colour). In this specific case, the curve was "
"recognized as a single segment and a single mouse-click on this segment is "
"sufficient to digitize this curve and to automatically place points along "
"the curve."
msgstr ""
"Postopek za pridobivanje podatkov iz uvožene ploskve, kot je opisan zgoraj, "
"je izvedljiv pri omejenem številu točk. Če so krivulje na uvoženi sliki "
"podane kot polne črte, orodje izvlečnik podatkov v &LabPlot; omogoča njihovo "
"(pol)samodejno branje. Za to, potem ko je bila dodana nova krivulja "
"izvlečnika podatkov, kot je opisano zgoraj, preklopite na način miške "
"\"Izberi segmente krivulje\". Krivulje na ploskvi so prepoznane in "
"poudarjene. S klikom na označeno krivuljo (ali enega od njenih segmentov) se "
"ustvarijo točke vzdolž te krivulje. Dolžina segmenta in gostota ustvarjenih "
"točk (razmik med dvema točkama) sta nastavljiva parametra. Na spodnjih "
"posnetkih zaslona so bile po preklopu v segmentni način vse črne črte "
"označene (zelena barva). V tem specifičnem primeru je bila krivulja "
"prepoznana kot en segment in en sam klik z miško na ta segment zadostuje za "
"digitalizacijo te krivulje in samodejno postavitev točk vzdolž krivulje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:575
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In many cases the plot is not as simple as above (single black curve on "
"white background) and contains grid lines, many curves of different colour "
"and thinness and a non-white background. In such a case the automatic "
"detection fails (too many or no objects are highlighted). To help the "
"datapicker to determine the curve(s) correctly, the user has to limit the "
"allowed ranges in the HSV (or HSI) colour spaces. To subtract the non-white "
"background it is possible to limit the range for the foreground colour, too. "
"Internally, each pixel of the image is converted to black and white where "
"only the points fitting into the user-defined ranges for hue, saturation, "
"value, intensity and foreground are set to black."
msgstr ""
"V mnogih primerih grafikon ni tako preprost kot zgoraj (ena črna krivulja na "
"belem ozadju) in vsebuje mrežne črte, številne krivulje različnih barv in "
"debelin ter nebelo ozadje. V tem primeru samodejno zaznavanje ne deluje "
"(označenih je preveč ali noben predmet). Da bi izvlečniku podatkov pomagali "
"pravilno določiti krivuljo(e), mora uporabnik omejiti dovoljene obsege v "
"barvnih prostorih HSV (ali HSI). Če želite odšteti nebelo ozadje, je mogoče "
"omejiti tudi obseg za barvo ospredja. Interno se vsaka slikovna pika slike "
"pretvori v črno-belo, pri čemer so samo točke, ki ustrezajo uporabniško "
"določenim razponom za odtenek, nasičenost, vrednost, intenzivnost in "
"ospredje, nastavljene na črno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:582
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the screenshots below, the blue curves in the original image were "
"projected onto by having appropriately reduced the allowed ranges in the "
"colour space (note the peak for blue in the histogram for the hue). The "
"transformed black and white image contains only the curves the user is "
"interested in and it is now an easy task for the datapicker to determine the "
"curves and to place points on them."
msgstr ""
"Na spodnjih posnetkih zaslona so bile modre krivulje na izvirni sliki "
"projicirane z ustreznim zmanjšanjem dovoljenih obsegov v barvnem prostoru "
"(upoštevajte vrh za modro v histogramu za odtenek). Preoblikovana črno-bela "
"slika vsebuje samo krivulje, ki uporabnika zanimajo, in izvlečniku podatkov "
"je zdaj enostavna naloga, da določi krivulje in nanje postavi točke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:590
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Similar to <link linkend=\"worksheet\">Worksheet</link>, the currently "
"visible area in the datapicker can be exported. The supported image formats "
"as described in the section <link linkend=\"exportdialog\">Export Dialog</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"Podobno kot <link linkend=\"worksheet\">Delovni list</link> je mogoče "
"trenutno vidno območje v izvlečniku podatkov izvoziti. Podprti formati slik, "
"kot so opisani v razdelku <link linkend=\"exportdialog\">Pogovorno okno za "
"izvoz</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:597
#, no-c-format
msgid "Import Dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za uvoz"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:598
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the import dialog you can import data into one of the available "
"spreadsheets or matrices in &LabPlot;. The supported data formats are "
"<itemizedlist> <listitem><para>ASCII</para></listitem> "
"<listitem><para>Binary</para></listitem> <listitem><para>Image</para></"
"listitem> <listitem><para>NetCDF</para></listitem> <listitem><para>HDF5</"
"para></listitem> <listitem><para>FITS</para></listitem> </itemizedlist> "
"Preview of all supported file types is available in the import dialog. For "
"data formats with complex internal structures (like NetCDF, HDF5 and FITS), "
"the content of the file is presented in a tree view that allows comfortable "
"navigation through the file. A versatile dialog to edit the headers "
"(keywords) of a FITS file is also provided."
msgstr ""
"V pogovornem oknu za uvoz lahko uvozite podatke v eno od razpoložljivih "
"preglednic ali matrik v &LabPlot;. Podprti formati podatkov so "
"<itemizedlist> <listitem><para>ASCII</para></listitem> "
"<listitem><para>Binarni</para></listitem> <listitem><para>Slika</para></"
"listitem> <listitem><para>NetCDF</para></listitem> <listitem><para>HDF5</"
"para></listitem> <listitem><para>FITS</para></listitem> </itemizedlist> "
"Predogled vseh podprtih vrst datotek je na voljo v pogovornem oknu za uvoz. "
"Za formate podatkov s kompleksno notranjo strukturo (kot so NetCDF, HDF5 in "
"FITS) je vsebina datoteke predstavljena v drevesnem pogledu, ki omogoča "
"udobno krmarjenje po datoteki. Na voljo je tudi vsestransko pogovorno okno "
"za urejanje glav (ključnih besed) datoteke FITS."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:616
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Import of ascii and binary data compressed with gzip, bzip2 or xz can be "
"done directly as the decompression happens transparently for the user."
msgstr ""
"Uvoz ascii in binarnih podatkov, stisnjenih z gzip, bzip2 ali xz, je mogoče "
"izvesti neposredno, saj dekompresija poteka pregledno za uporabnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:621
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The name of the file containing the data to import has to be provided. The "
"<guibutton>File Info</guibutton> button opens a dialog where some "
"information about the selected file is shown. The type of the data can be "
"specified - currently, only ASCII files containing several data sets "
"(vectors) stored as columns are supported. The filter - automatic or custom "
"- determines how the file has to be parsed. Selecting the filter \"custom\", "
"several parameters like separating character &etc; can be provided manually "
"in this case."
msgstr ""
"Navesti je treba ime datoteke, ki vsebuje podatke za uvoz. Gumb "
"<guibutton>Informacije o datoteki</guibutton> odpre pogovorno okno, v "
"katerem so prikazane nekatere informacije o izbrani datoteki. Tip podatkov "
"je mogoče določiti - trenutno so podprte samo datoteke ASCII, ki vsebujejo "
"več naborov podatkov (vektorjev), shranjenih kot stolpci. Filter – samodejni "
"ali po meri – določa, kako je treba datoteko razčleniti. Izbira filtra \"po "
"meri\", več parametrov, kot je ločilni znak &etc; v tem primeru lahko "
"zagotovite ročno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:625
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The start and end row to read can be customized using the <guilabel>Data "
"portion to read</guilabel> tab. To read all data specify <userinput>-1</"
"userinput> as an end row or column."
msgstr ""
"Začetno in končno vrstico za branje lahko prilagodite z uporabo zavihka "
"<guilabel>Podatkovni del za branje</guilabel>. Če želite prebrati vse "
"podatke, podajte <userinput>-1</userinput> kot končno vrstico ali stolpec."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:629
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Importing data into &LabPlot;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Uvažanje podatkov v &LabPlot;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:635
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Importing data into &LabPlot;</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Uvažanje podatkov v &LabPlot;</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:644
#, no-c-format
msgid "Export Dialog"
msgstr "Izvozno pogovorno okno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:645
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A worksheet can be exported to several graphics format (vector and raster). "
"The export is done via the export dialog reachable via the "
"<guibutton>Export</guibutton> in the main toolbar or "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Export</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> in the main menu."
msgstr ""
"Delovni list je mogoče izvoziti v več grafičnih formatov (vektorskih in "
"rastrskih). Izvoz se izvede prek pogovornega okna za izvoz, ki ga lahko "
"dosežete prek <guibutton>Izvoz</guibutton> v glavni orodni vrstici ali "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izvoz</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> v glavnem meniju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:652
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Besides the graphics format, the user can specify which part of the "
"worksheet has to be exported and whether the background has to be exported "
"or not. Also, for raster graphics the image resolution can be provided."
msgstr ""
"Poleg grafične oblike lahko uporabnik določi, kateri del delovnega lista naj "
"se izvozi in ali naj se izvozi ozadje ali ne. Za rastrsko grafiko je tudi "
"mogoče zagotoviti ločljivost slike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:662
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The content of a spreadsheet can be exported to an external text or FITS "
"file. In the export dialog for spreadsheets the user can specify the "
"character separating values of different columns. Optionally, the header of "
"the spreadsheet (names of the columns in the spreadsheet) can be exported."
msgstr ""
"Vsebino preglednice je mogoče izvoziti v zunanjo besedilno datoteko ali "
"datoteko FITS. V pogovornem oknu za izvoz preglednic lahko uporabnik določi "
"vrednosti, ki ločujejo znake v različnih stolpcih. Po želji je mogoče "
"izvoziti glavo preglednice (imena stolpcev v preglednici)."

