msgstr "Ustvari novo &LabPlot; projektno datoteko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:692
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In a project file all settings and all plots are stored in ASCII format."
msgstr ""
"V projektni datoteki so vse nastavitve in vsi grafikoni shranjeni v formatu "
"ASCII."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:697
