#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:718
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saves the actual project."
msgstr "Shrani dejanski projekt."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:719
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you haven't saved the project before the project is saved under a "
"temporary project file name."
msgstr ""
"Če projekta niste shranili, preden se projekt shrani pod imenom začasne "
"projektne datoteke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:724
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save As</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani kot</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:727
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saves the actual project under a different name."
msgstr "Shrani dejanski projekt pod drugim imenom."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:733
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Print</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Natisni</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:737
#, no-c-format
msgid "Prints the active plot."
msgstr "Natisne aktivni izris."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:738
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here a print dialog is opened where you can select the printer, different "
"paper sizes, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Tukaj se odpre pogovorno okno za tiskanje, kjer lahko izberete tiskalnik, "
"različne velikosti papirja &etc;"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:745
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Print Preview</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Predogled tiskanja</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:748
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Open a print preview window.</action> &LabPlot; allows you to choose "
"print settings using the toolbar of this window and view the result "
"immediately."
msgstr ""
"<action>Odpri okno za predogled tiskanja.</action> &LabPlot; omogoča izbiro "
"nastavitev tiskanja v orodni vrstici tega okna in takojšnji ogled rezultata."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:753
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>=</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Spreadsheet</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>=</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Nova</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Preglednica</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:757 index.docbook:774
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creates a new spreadsheet in the current folder of &LabPlot; project."
msgstr "Ustvari novo preglednico v trenutni mapi &LabPlot; projektov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:762
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Worksheet</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Novo</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Delovni "
"list</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:766
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creates a new worksheet in the current folder of &LabPlot; project."
msgstr "Ustvari nov delovni list v trenutni mapi &LabPlot; projektov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:771
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Folder</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Nova</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Mapa</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:779
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>File Data "
"Source</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Nova</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Datotečni vir podatkov</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:782
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens <guilabel>Import data to spreadsheet/matrix</guilabel> window."
msgstr "Odpre okno <guilabel>Uvoz podatkov v preglednico/matriko</guilabel>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:787
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Import</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Uvoz</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:792
#, no-c-format
msgid "Import data into the active spreadsheet"
msgstr "Uvozi podatke v aktivno preglednico"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:793
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This item can be used to import data into &LabPlot;. Please read more in the "
"<link linkend=\"importdialog\">import dialog</link> section."
msgstr ""
"Ta element se lahko uporablja za uvoz podatkov v &LabPlot;. Preberite več v "
"razdelku <link linkend=\"importdialog\">pogovorno okno uvoza</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:801
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Export</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izvoz</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:804
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saves the active plot as special format."
msgstr "Shrani aktivni grafikon kot poseben format."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:805
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Currently supported are Encapsulated Postscript (EPS), Portable Document "
"Format (PDF), Scalable Vector Graphics (SVG) and Portable Network Graphics "
"(PNG)."
msgstr ""
"Trenutno so podprti Encapsulated Postscript (EPS), Portable Document Format "
"(PDF), Scalable Vector Graphics (SVG) in Portable Network Graphics (PNG)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:809
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Close</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:813
#, no-c-format
msgid "Closes the current opened &LabPlot; project file."
msgstr "Zapre trenutno odprto &LabPlot; projektno datoteko."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:818
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:822
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quit &LabPlot;."
msgstr "Zapri &LabPlot;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:830
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Edit Menu"
msgstr "Meni Urejanje"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:835
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Undo/Redo History</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zgodovina razveljavi/uveljavi</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:838
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Opens the &LabPlot; action history window.</action> Select an item "
"in the list to navigate to the corresponding step."
msgstr ""
"<action>Odpre &LabPlot; okno zgodovine dejanj.</action> Izbere element na "
"seznamu, da se pomakne do ustreznega koraka."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:846
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Worksheet Menu"
msgstr "Meni delovnega lista"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:847
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu contains all the items that can also be found in the context menu "
"(right mouse) of a worksheet. The menu is only available when a worksheet "
"object is selected on the <guilabel>Project Explorer</guilabel> panel."
msgstr ""
"Ta meni vsebuje vse elemente, ki jih lahko najdete tudi v kontekstnem meniju "
"(desna miška) delovnega lista. Meni je na voljo samo, ko je predmet "
"delovnega lista izbran na plošči <guilabel>Raziskovalec projektov</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:854
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Spreadsheet Menu"
msgstr "Meni preglednice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:855
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu contains all the items that can also be found in the context menu "
"(right mouse) of a spreadsheet. The menu is only available when a "
"spreadsheet object is selected on the <guilabel>Project Explorer</guilabel> "
"panel."
msgstr ""
"Ta meni vsebuje vse elemente, ki jih lahko najdete tudi v kontekstnem meniju "
"(desna miška) preglednice. Meni je na voljo le, ko je na plošči "
"<guilabel>Raziskovalec projektov</guilabel> izbran predmet preglednice."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:862
#, no-c-format
msgid "The CAS Worksheet Menu"
msgstr "Meni delovnega lista CAS"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:863
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu contains all the items that can also be found in the context menu "
"(right mouse) of a CAS worksheet. The menu is only available when a "
"worksheet object is selected on the <guilabel>Project Explorer</guilabel> "
"panel."
msgstr ""
"Ta meni vsebuje vse elemente, ki jih lahko najdete tudi v kontekstnem meniju "
"(desna miška) delovnega lista CAS. Meni je na voljo samo, ko je predmet "
"delovnega lista izbran na plošči <guilabel>Raziskovalec projektov</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:869
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Datapicker Menu"
msgstr "Meni izvlečnika podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:870
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu contains all the items that can also be found in the context menu "
"(right mouse) of a datapicker. The menu is only available when a datapicker "
"object is selected on the <guilabel>Project Explorer</guilabel> panel."
msgstr ""
"Ta meni vsebuje vse elemente, ki jih lahko najdete tudi v kontekstnem meniju "
"(desna miška) izvlečnika podatkov. Meni je na voljo le, ko je na plošči "
"<guilabel>Raziskovalec projektov</guilabel> izbran predmet izvlečnika "
"podatkov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:877
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings Menu"
msgstr "Meni Nastavitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:879
#, no-c-format
msgid "This menu gives you the ability to change user settings."
msgstr "Ta meni vam omogoča spreminjanje uporabniških nastavitev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:881
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Apart from the common &kde; Settings menu entries described in the <ulink "
"url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">Settings Menu</ulink> "
"chapter of the &kde; Fundamentals &LabPlot; has this application specific "
"menu entry:"
msgstr ""
"Poleg običajnega &kde; Vnosi menija z nastavitvami, opisani v poglavju "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">Meni z "
"nastavitvami</ulink> v &kde; Osnove &LabPlot; ima ta aplikacija še poseben "
"vnos v meniju:"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:885
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Full Screen Mode</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Celozaslonski način</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:889
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show the workspace in full screen mode."
msgstr "Prikaže delovni prostor v celozaslonskem načinu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:897
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Help Menu"
msgstr "Meni Pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:899
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally, &LabPlot; has the common &kde; Help menu items. For more "
"information, read the section about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/"
"menus.html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega &LabPlot; ima skupno &kde; Elemente menija za pomoč. Za več "
"informacij preberite razdelek o <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">meniju Pomoč</ulink> programa &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:906
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toolbar"
msgstr "Orodna vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:908
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The main toolbar contains the main items that you can find in the different "
"menus. More details on this can be found in the <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/config.html#toolbars\">&kde; Fundamentals manual</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Glavna orodna vrstica vsebuje glavne elemente, ki jih najdete v različnih "
"menijih. Več podrobnosti o tem lahko najdete v <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/config.html#toolbars\">&kde; Priročnik o osnovah</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:915
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plotting"
msgstr "Risanje"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:918
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plots"
msgstr "Izrisi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:919
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Plots can be created inside a worksheet via \"Add new\" in the context menu "
"or in the application menu via \"Worksheet\" by selecting \"xy-plot\" and "
"the type of plot you like to have."
msgstr ""
"Izrise lahko ustvarite znotraj delovnega lista prek možnosti »Dodaj novo« v "
"kontekstnem meniju ali v meniju aplikacije prek »Delovni list«, tako da "
"izberete »xy-krivulja« in vrsto izrisa, ki ga želite imeti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:923
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Within this xy-plot you can add a xy-curve containing data to show (again "
"via the context menu or application menu)."
msgstr ""
"Znotraj te xy-krivulje lahko dodate xy-krivuljo, ki vsebuje podatke za "
"prikaz (spet prek kontekstnega menija ali menija aplikacije)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:926
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The settings of a plot can be changed in the corresponding dock widget. "
"There are general settings like geometry but also the range of the x- and y-"
"axis (including scaling). The plot title can be set in the \"Title\" tab of "
"the dock widget. Background and border styles can be changed in the \"Plot "
"Area\" tab."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve izrisa lahko spremenite v ustreznem gradniku doka. Obstajajo "
"splošne nastavitve, kot je geometrija, pa tudi obseg osi x in y (vključno s "
"prilagoditvijo lestvice). Naslov ploskve lahko nastavite na zavihku »Naslov« "
"gradnika doka. Sloge ozadja in obrob lahko spremenite v zavihku \"Območje "
"izrisa\"."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:934
#, no-c-format
msgid "Curves"
msgstr "Krivulje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:935
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Curves contain data points that can be shown in a plot. There are three "
"different method to create curves: the standard xy-curve, a xy-curve from a "
"mathematical expression and a xy-curve from a data analysis function."
msgstr ""
"Krivulje vsebujejo podatkovne točke, ki jih je mogoče prikazati na izrisu. "
"Obstajajo tri različne metode za ustvarjanje krivulj: standardna xy-"
"krivulja, xy-krivulja iz matematičnega izraza in xy-krivulja iz funkcije "
"analize podatkov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:940
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The standard xy-curve can be filled with values of a spreadsheet by "
"selecting the x-data and y-data as column of the spreadsheet in the xy-curve "
"dock widget. Another method to fill a curve is to use a mathematical "
"expression. Here you can select any mathematical function and range to "
"create the curve. The third method to create a curve is to use a data "
"analysis function. The data and the analysis function can be selected in the "
"dock widget of the analysis function."
msgstr ""
"Standardno krivuljo xy lahko napolnite z vrednostmi preglednice tako, da "
"izberete podatke x in podatke y kot stolpca preglednice v pripomočku za "
"priklop krivulje xy. Druga metoda za zapolnitev krivulje je uporaba "
"matematičnega izraza. Tukaj lahko izberete katero koli matematično funkcijo "
"in obseg za ustvarjanje krivulje. Tretja metoda za ustvarjanje krivulje je "
"uporaba funkcije za analizo podatkov. Podatke in funkcijo analize lahko "
"izberete v gradniku doka analizne funkcije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:947
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For all types of curves the line and symbols styles can be changed in the "
"dock widget. Also annotated values and error bar settings can be changed "
"here."
msgstr ""
"Za vse vrste krivulj je mogoče spremeniti sloge črt in simbolov v gradniku "
"doka. Tukaj lahko spremenite tudi označene vrednosti in nastavitve vrstice "
"napak."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:954
#, no-c-format
msgid "Legends"
msgstr "Legende"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:955
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A legend can be easily added to a plot by using the context of application "
"menu. It contains information about all curves in a plot."
msgstr ""
"Legendo je mogoče preprosto dodati izrisu z uporabo konteksta menija "
"aplikacije. Vsebuje informacije o vseh krivuljah na izrisu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:959
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The settings of a legend (format and geometry) can be changed in the legend "
"dock widget. Also the legend title settings, the legend background and the "
"layout can be changed in the corresponding tab of the legend dock widget."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve legende (format in geometrijo) lahko spremenite v gradniku doka "
"za legende. Prav tako je mogoče spremeniti nastavitve naslova legende, "
"ozadje legende in postavitev na ustreznem zavihku gradnika doka legende."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:968
#, no-c-format
msgid "Analysis functions"
msgstr "Funkcije analize"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:970
#, no-c-format
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Pregled"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:971
#, no-c-format
msgid "&LabPlot; supports a wide variety of data analysis functions:"
msgstr "&LabPlot; podpira široko paleto funkcij za analizo podatkov:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:975
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Data reduction</para>"
msgstr "<para>Zmanjšanje podatkov</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:976
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Differentiation</para>"
msgstr "<para>Odvajanje</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:977
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Integration</para>"
msgstr "<para>Integracija</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:978
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Interpolation</para>"
msgstr "<para>Interpolacija</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:979
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Smoothing</para>"
msgstr "<para>Glajenje</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:980
#, no-c-format
msgid "Nonlinear curve fitting"
msgstr "Prileganje nelinearne krivulje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:981
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Fourier filter</para>"
msgstr "<para>Fourierjev filter</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:982
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Fourier transform</para>"
msgstr "<para>Fourierjeva transformacija</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:984
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All of them can be applied to any data consisting of x- and y-columns. The "
"analysis functions can be accessed using the Analysis menu or the context "
"menu of a worksheet. The newly created curves can be customized (line style, "
"symbol style, &etc;) like any other x-y-curve."
msgstr ""
"Vse jih je mogoče uporabiti za vse podatke, sestavljene iz stolpcev x in y. "
"Do funkcij analize lahko dostopate z uporabo menija Analiza ali kontekstnega "
"menija delovnega lista. Novo ustvarjene krivulje je mogoče prilagoditi (slog "
"črte, slog simbola itd.) kot vsako drugo krivuljo x-y."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:992
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Data reduction</title>"
msgstr "<title>Zmanjšanje podatkov</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:993
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To reduce the number of data points without losing the features of a data "
"set you can apply one of several line simplification algorithm:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite zmanjšati število podatkovnih točk, ne da bi pri tem izgubili "
"značilnosti nabora podatkov, lahko uporabite enega od več algoritmov za "
"poenostavitev vrstic:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:998
#, no-c-format
msgid "Douglas-Peucker"
msgstr "Douglas-Peucker"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:999
#, no-c-format
msgid "Visvalingam-Whyatt"
msgstr "Visvalingam-Whyatt"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1000
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reumann-Witkam"
msgstr "Reumann-Witkam"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1001
#, no-c-format
msgid "Perpendicular distance simplification"
msgstr "Poenostavitev pravokotne razdalje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1002
#, no-c-format
msgid "n-th point simplification"
msgstr "n-ta poenostavitev točke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1003
#, no-c-format
msgid "Radial distance simplification"
msgstr "Poenostavitev radialne razdalje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1004
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interpolation (nearest neighbor)"
msgstr "Interpolacija (najbližji sosed)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1005
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opheim"
msgstr "Opheim"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1006
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lang"
msgstr "Lang"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1008
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The desired tolerance is automatically calculated from the data but can also "
"be changed in the dock widget."
msgstr ""
"Želena toleranca se samodejno izračuna iz podatkov, lahko pa jo tudi "
"spremenite v gradniku doka."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1015
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Differentiation</title>"
msgstr "<title>Odvajanje</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1016
#, no-c-format
msgid "Numerical differentiation of data can be done specifying:"
msgstr "Numerično odvajanje podatkov je mogoče izvesti z navedbo:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1020
#, no-c-format
msgid "order of derivation (first to sixth order)"
msgstr "vrstni red odvajanja (prvi do šesti vrstni red)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1021
#, no-c-format
msgid "order of accuracy (up to 4th order, depending on derivation order)"
msgstr "vrstni red točnosti (do 4. reda, odvisno od vrstnega reda odvajanja)"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1026
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Integration</title>"
msgstr "<title>Integracija</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1027
#, no-c-format
msgid "Numerical integration of data can be done specifying one of the methods"
msgstr "Numerično integracijo podatkov lahko izvedemo z navedbo ene od metod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1031
#, no-c-format
msgid "rectangle (1-point) rule"
msgstr "pravilo pravokotnika (1-točka)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1032
#, no-c-format
msgid "trapezoid (2-point) rule"
msgstr "trapezoid (2-točkovno) pravilo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1033
#, no-c-format
msgid "Simpson-1/3 (3-point) rule"
msgstr "Simpsonovo pravilo 1/3 (3 točke)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1034
#, no-c-format
msgid "Simpson-3/8 (4-point) rule"
msgstr "Simpsonovo pravilo 3/8 (4 točke)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1036
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default method (trapezoid) should be suitable for most cases. The number "
"of resulting data points is reduced for both Simpson-rules due to the "
"properties of these methods."
msgstr ""
"Privzeta metoda (trapezoid) bi morala biti primerna za večino primerov. "
"Število nastalih podatkovnih točk je zmanjšano za obe Simpsonovi pravili "
"zaradi lastnosti teh metod."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1043
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Interpolation</title>"
msgstr "<title>Interpolacija</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1044
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interpolation of data can be done with several algorithm:"
msgstr "Interpolacijo podatkov lahko izvedemo z več algoritmi:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1048
#, no-c-format
msgid "linear"
msgstr "linearni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1049
#, no-c-format
msgid "polynomial (if number of data points &lt; 100)"
msgstr "polinomski (če je število podatkovnih točk &lt; 100)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1050
#, no-c-format
msgid "cubic spline"
msgstr "kubični zlepek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1051
#, no-c-format
msgid "cubic spline (periodic)"
msgstr "kubični zlepek (periodični)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1052
#, no-c-format
msgid "Akima spline"
msgstr "Akima zlepek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1053
#, no-c-format
msgid "Akima spline (periodic)"
msgstr "Akima zlepek (periodični)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1054
#, no-c-format
msgid "Steffen spline (needs GSL &ge; 2.0)"
msgstr "Steffenov zlepek (potrebuje GSL &ge; 2.0)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1055
#, no-c-format
msgid "cosine"
msgstr "kosinus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1056
#, no-c-format
msgid "exponential"
msgstr "eksponentni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1057
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"piecewise cubic Hermite (finite differences, Catmull-Rom, cardinal, Kochanek-"
"Bartels)"
msgstr ""
"odsekoma kubični Hermit (končne diference, Catmull-Rom, kardinal, Kochanek-"
"Bartels)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1058
#, no-c-format
msgid "rational functions"
msgstr "racionalne funkcije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1060
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The interpolating function is calculated with the given number n of data "
"points and evaluated as:"
msgstr ""
"Interpolacijska funkcija se izračuna z danim številom podatkovnih točk n in "
"ovrednoti kot:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1064
#, no-c-format
msgid "function"
msgstr "funkcija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1065
#, no-c-format
msgid "derivative"
msgstr "odvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1066
#, no-c-format
msgid "second derivative"
msgstr "drugi odvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1067
#, no-c-format
msgid "integral (starting from zero)"
msgstr "integral (začenši od nič)"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1072
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Smoothing</title>"
msgstr "<title>Glajenje</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1073
#, no-c-format
msgid "A number of different smoothing methods are supported:"
msgstr "Podprtih je več različnih metod glajenja:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1077
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moving average (central)"
msgstr "Drseče povprečje (osrednje)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1078
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moving average (lagged)"
msgstr "Drseče povprečje (z zamikom)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1079
#, no-c-format
msgid "Percentile filter"
msgstr "Percentilni filter"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1080
#, no-c-format
msgid "Savitzky-Golay"
msgstr "Savitzky-Golay"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1082
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All smoothing methods support several padding modes (constant, periodic, "
"mirror, nearest, etc.) for the beginning and end of the data set. The moving "
"averages support several weight functions (uniform, triangular, binomial, "
"parabolic, tricubic, etc.) which can be selected to weight the selected data "
"points depending on their distance."
msgstr ""
"Vse metode glajenja podpirajo več načinov polnjenja (konstantno, periodično, "
"zrcalno, najbližje itd.) za začetek in konec niza podatkov. Drseča povprečja "
"podpirajo več utežnih funkcij (enakomerno, trikotno, binomsko, parabolično, "
"trikubično itd.), ki jih je mogoče izbrati za uteževanje izbranih "
"podatkovnih točk glede na njihovo oddaljenost."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1090
#, no-c-format
msgid "Curve fitting"
msgstr "Prileganje krivulj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1091
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Linear and non-linear curve fitting of data can be done with several "
"predefined fit-models (for instance polynomial, exponential, Gaussian or "
"custom) to data consisting of x- and y-columns with an optional weight "
"column. With a custom model any function with unlimited number of parameters "
"can be used for fitting. The results including statistical properties are "
"displayed in the results text."
msgstr ""
"Linearno in nelinearno prilagajanje krivulj podatkov je mogoče izvesti z več "
"vnaprej določenimi modeli prilagajanja (na primer polinomski, eksponentni, "
"Gaussov ali po meri) na podatke, sestavljene iz stolpcev x in y z izbirnim "
"stolpcem teže. Z modelom po meri se lahko za prilagajanje uporabi katera "
"koli funkcija z neomejenim številom parametrov. Rezultati, vključno s "
"statističnimi lastnostmi, so prikazani v besedilu rezultatov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1097
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The start values of the parameter can be set in the parameter dialog. It is "
"also possible to fix any parameter and set lower and upper limits to the "
"values here. Be aware that reducing the parameter space by fixing parameter "
"or specifying limits can slow down convergence or avoid finding a good "
"result. It's always a good idea to remove any parameter limitations when "
"good start values are found."
msgstr ""
"Začetne vrednosti parametra lahko nastavite v pogovornem oknu parametrov. "
"Prav tako je mogoče popraviti kateri koli parameter in nastaviti spodnjo in "
"zgornjo mejo vrednosti tukaj. Zavedajte se, da lahko zmanjšanje prostora "
"parametrov s fiksiranjem parametrov ali določanjem omejitev upočasni "
"konvergenco ali prepreči iskanje dobrega rezultata. Ko so najdene dobre "
"začetne vrednosti, je vedno dobro odstraniti vse omejitve parametrov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Following options can be set in the options dialog to optimize the fitting:"
msgstr ""
"V pogovornem oknu z možnostmi lahko nastavite naslednje možnosti za "
"optimizacijo prileganja:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Max. iterations: number of maximum iterations"
msgstr "maks. iteracij: največje število ponovitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1105
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tolerance: desired tolerance for result"
msgstr "Toleranca: želena toleranca za rezultat"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1106
#, no-c-format
msgid "Evaluated points: number of points to evaluate the fit function"
msgstr "Ovrednotene točke: število točk za oceno funkcije prileganja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Evaluate full range: evaluate the fit function for the full data range "
"instead of evaluating only for the given x range"
msgstr ""
"Ocenite celoten obseg: ovrednotite funkcijo prileganja za celoten obseg "
"podatkov namesto vrednotenja samo za dani obseg x"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use results as new start values: results will be the new parameter start "
"values"
msgstr ""
"Uporabi rezultate kot nove začetne vrednosti: rezultati bodo nove začetne "
"vrednosti parametrov"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1114
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Fourier filter</title>"
msgstr "<title>Fourierjev filter</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This function can be used to apply a Fourier filter to any data consisting "
"of x- and y-columns. Supported filter types are:"
msgstr ""
"To funkcijo lahko uporabite za uporabo Fourierjevega filtra za vse podatke, "
"sestavljene iz stolpcev x in y. Podprte vrste filtrov so:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Low pass"
msgstr "Nizka prepustnost"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1121
#, no-c-format
msgid "High pass"
msgstr "Visoka prepustnost"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1122
#, no-c-format
msgid "Band pass"
msgstr "Intervalna prepustnost"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1123
#, no-c-format
msgid "Band reject (band block)"
msgstr "Zavrnitev v pasu (blok pasu)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1125
#, no-c-format
msgid "where any of them can have the form"
msgstr "kjer ima lahko katera koli od njih obliko"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ideal"
msgstr "Idealno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1130
#, no-c-format
msgid "Butterworth (order 1 to 10)"
msgstr "Butterworth (vrstni red od 1 do 10)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Chebyshev type I or II (order 1 to 10)"
msgstr "Čebišev tip I ali II (vrstni red 1 do 10)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1132
#, no-c-format
msgid "Optimal \"L\"egendre (order 1 to 10)"
msgstr "Optimalni \"L\"egendre (vrstni red 1 do 10)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1133
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bessel-Thomson (any order)"
msgstr "Bessel-Thomson (kateri koli vrstni red)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The cutoff value(s) can be specified in the units frequency (Hertz), "
"fraction (0.0 to 1.0) or index of the data points."
msgstr ""
"Mejne vrednosti je mogoče določiti v frekvenci enot (herci), frakciji (0,0 "
"do 1,0) ali indeksu podatkovnih točk."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1142
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Fourier transform</title>"
msgstr "<title>Fourierjeva transformacija</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To convert a signal from time to frequency domain or to change between other "
"conjugate variables like position and momentum (k-space) a discrete Fourier "
"transform can be applied. Following options can be used to suite one needs:"
msgstr ""
"Za pretvorbo signala iz časovne v frekvenčno domeno ali za preklop med "
"drugimi konjugiranimi spremenljivkami, kot sta položaj in zagon (k-prostor), "
"je mogoče uporabiti diskretno Fourierjevo transformacijo. Naslednje možnosti "
"je mogoče uporabiti za zadovoljitev potreb:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1149
#, no-c-format
msgid "Window function (Welch, Hann, Hamming, etc.) to avoid leakage effects"
msgstr ""
"Funkcija okna (Welch, Hann, Hamming itd.), da se izognete učinkom puščanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1150
#, no-c-format
msgid "Output (magnitude, amplitude, phase, dB, etc.)"
msgstr "Izhod (magnituda, amplituda, faza, dB itd.)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1151
#, no-c-format
msgid "One or two sided spectrum with or without shifting"
msgstr "Eno ali dvostranski spekter s premikom ali brez njega"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1152
#, no-c-format
msgid "X axis scaling to frequency, index or period"
msgstr "Lestvici prilagojena os X na frekvenco, indeks ali obdobje"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1158
#, no-c-format
msgid "Curve Tracing"
msgstr "Sledenje krivulji"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1161
#, no-c-format
msgid "Upload Image"
msgstr "Prenesi sliko"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Datapicker can be created inside a project via <guimenuitem>Add new</"
"guimenuitem> in the context menu of project/folder or in the main toolbar. "
"After that a new image can be added and can be changed via <guilabel>Plot</"
"guilabel> in the corresponding dock widget."
msgstr ""
"Izvlečnik podatkov lahko ustvarite znotraj projekta prek <guimenuitem>Dodaj "
"novo</guimenuitem> v kontekstnem meniju projekta/mape ali v glavni orodni "
"vrstici. Po tem je mogoče dodati novo sliko in jo spremeniti prek "
"<guilabel>Izris</guilabel> v ustreznem gradniku doka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After uploading image different zooming options can be used from the context "
"menu/datapicker toolbar to change width and height of image. Image can also "
"be rotated to an angle using <guilabel>Rotation</guilabel> in the \"edit\" "
"section of dock widget. After this user have to <link linkend=\"axispoint"
"\">set axis points</link>."
msgstr ""
"Po nalaganju slike lahko uporabite različne možnosti povečave v kontekstnem "
"meniju/orodni vrstici izvlečnika podatkov, da spremenite širino in višino "
"slike. Sliko lahko tudi zasukate pod kotom z <guilabel>Rotacijo</guilabel> v "
"razdelku »urejanje« gradnika dok. Potem mora uporabnik <link linkend="
"\"axispoint\">nastaviti točke osi</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1174
#, no-c-format
msgid "Symbols"
msgstr "Simboli"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1175
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Symbols are the points that can be drawn over image of datapicker. Symbols "
"can be directly created by mouse right click over the image. Symbols are "
"mainly of two types, with and without error-bar depending on the type of "
"<link linkend=\"datapickercurve\">curve</link> they belong."
msgstr ""
"Simboli so točke, ki jih je mogoče narisati čez sliko izvlečnika podatkov. "
"Simbole lahko ustvarite neposredno z desnim klikom miške na sliko. Simboli "
"so večinoma dveh vrst, z in brez vrstice napak, odvisno od vrste <link "
"linkend=\"datapickercurve\">krivulje</link>, ki ji pripadajo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Every curve of datapicker can have its own symbol style that can be changed "
"in the <guilabel>Symbols</guilabel> section of dock widget. \"SelectAndMove"
"\" mouse mode can be used to select multiple points/symbols and can be moved "
"by using navigation keys."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka krivulja izvlečnika podatkov ima lahko svoj slog simbola, ki ga je "
"mogoče spremeniti v razdelku <guilabel>Simboli</guilabel> gradnika doka. "
"Način miške \"IzberiInPremakni\" lahko uporabite za izbiro več točk/simbolov "
"in jih lahko premikate z uporabo navigacijskih tipk."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1187
#, no-c-format
msgid "Axis Points"
msgstr "Točke osi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Axis Points are the set of three reference <link linkend=\"symbols\">points</"
"link> over image of datapicker. These points can be set via <guimenuitem>Set "
"Axis Points</guimenuitem> in the context menu of datapicker. After selecting "
"points over image user have to update their coordinate system type via "
"<guilabel>Plot Type</guilabel> and logical positions via <guilabel>Ref. "
"Points</guilabel> in the dock widget."
msgstr ""
"Točke osi so niz treh referenčnih <link linkend=\"symbols\">točk</link> nad "
"sliko izvlečnika podatkov. Te točke lahko nastavite prek "
"<guimenuitem>Nastavi osne točke</guimenuitem> v kontekstnem meniju "
"izvlečnika podatkov. Po izbiri točk na sliki mora uporabnik posodobiti svoj "
"tip koordinatnega sistema prek <guilabel>Vrsta izrisa</guilabel> in logične "
"položaje prek <guilabel>Ref. Točke</guilabel> v gradniku doka."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1196
#, no-c-format
msgid "Datapicker Curve"
msgstr "Krivulja izvlečnika podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Datapicker-Curve can be created inside datapicker via <guimenuitem>New "
"Curve</guimenuitem> in the context menu of datapicker. A curve can have "
"different types of X and Y errors (No-error, symmetric, asymmetric). This "
"depends on the type of errors dock widget of datapicker have at the point of "
"creation."
msgstr ""
"Krivulja izvlečnika podatkov se lahko ustvari znotraj izvlečnika podatkov "
"prek <guimenuitem>Nova krivulja</guimenuitem> v kontekstnem meniju "
"izvlečnika podatkov. Krivulja ima lahko različne vrste napak X in Y (brez "
"napake, simetrična, asimetrična). To je odvisno od vrste napak, ki jih ima "
"sidrni gradnik izvlečnika podatkov na točki ustvarjanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Every curve object contains all the curve <link linkend=\"symbols\">points</"
"link> (hidden) and a spreadsheet that contains logical positions of all its "
"curve points, and provides options to update spreadsheet and to toggle "
"visibility of its curve points using the context menu. Mode <guimenuitem>Set "
"Curve Points</guimenuitem> in the context menu of datapicker should be "
"selected in order to create curve points."
msgstr ""
"Vsak predmet krivulje vsebuje vse <link linkend=\"symbols\">točke</link> "
"krivulje (skrite) in preglednico, ki vsebuje logične položaje vseh točk "
"krivulje ter ponuja možnosti za posodobitev preglednice in preklop vidnosti "
"točk krivulje z uporabo kontekstnega menija. Za ustvarjanje točk krivulje "
"mora biti izbran način <guimenuitem>Nastavi točke krivulje</guimenuitem> v "
"kontekstnem meniju izvlečnika podatkov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Multiple curve can be created for same datapicker. The created curve points "
"always correspond to the active curve of datapicker which can be changed via "
"<guimenuitem>Active Curve</guimenuitem> option in the context menu and dock "
"widget of datapicker. Every curve of datapicker can have its own symbol "
"style that can be changed in the <guilabel>Symbols</guilabel> section of "
"dock widget."
msgstr ""
"Za isti izvlečnik podatkov je mogoče ustvariti več krivulj. Ustvarjene točke "
"krivulje vedno ustrezajo aktivni krivulji izvlečnika podatkov, ki jo je "
"mogoče spremeniti z možnostjo <guimenuitem>Aktivna krivulja</guimenuitem> v "
"kontekstnem meniju in zasidranem gradniku izvlečnika podatkov. Vsaka "
"krivulja izvlečnika podatkov ima lahko svoj slog simbola, ki ga je mogoče "
"spremeniti v razdelku <guilabel>Simboli</guilabel> gradnika doka."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1216
#, no-c-format
msgid "Curve Segments"
msgstr "Segmenti krivulje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1217
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Curve segment for datapicker can be created over image by switching mode to "
"<guimenuitem>Select Curve Segments</guimenuitem> in the context menu of "
"datapicker. A segment is a selectable object over image which can be "
"selected by mouse right click over it."
msgstr ""
"Segment krivulje za izvlečnik podatkov je mogoče ustvariti nad sliko tako, "
"da preklopite način na <guimenuitem>Izberi segmente krivulje</guimenuitem> v "
"kontekstnem meniju izvlečnika podatkov. Segment je izbrani predmet nad "
"sliko, ki ga lahko izberete z desnim klikom miške nad njim."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1221
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Segments are created by processing of image on the basis range of colour "
"attributes in order to automatically trace curves. To improve results these "
"range and types of colour attributes can be changed in the \"edit\" section "
"of dock-widget. Dock-widget also provides options to switch among processed "
"image and original image, and to set the minimum possible length of segments."
msgstr ""
"Segmenti so ustvarjeni z obdelavo slike na podlagi obsega barvnih atributov "
"za samodejno sledenje krivuljam. Če želite izboljšati rezultate, lahko ta "
"obseg in vrste barvnih atributov spremenite v razdelku »urejanje« gradnika "
"doka. Gradnik doka ponuja tudi možnosti za preklapljanje med obdelano sliko "
"in izvirno sliko ter za nastavitev najmanjše možne dolžine segmentov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once a segment is selected it will create curve points over it with a "
"minimum specified distance among them. The minimum specified distance among "
"the points can be changed in the dock widget of datapicker. User might have "
"to select the segments again in order to observe the changes."
msgstr ""
"Ko je segment izbran, bo nad njim ustvaril točke krivulje z minimalno "
"določeno razdaljo med njimi. Najmanjšo določeno razdaljo med točkami je "
"mogoče spremeniti v gradniku doka izvlečnika podatkov. Uporabnik bo morda "
"moral znova izbrati segmente, da bo lahko opazoval spremembe."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1246
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced Topics"
msgstr "Napredne teme"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1247
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you will find some explanations of advanced topics."
msgstr "Tukaj boste našli nekaj razlag naprednih tem."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1252
#, no-c-format
msgid "Topics"
msgstr "Teme"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1254
#, no-c-format
msgid "Error bars"
msgstr "Črte napak"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to plot data with error bars just import your data with the "
"<link linkend=\"importdialog\">import dialog</link> into your project. Then "
"use the <guilabel>Error bars</guilabel> tab of <link linkend=\"properties-"
"explorer\">the curve properties</link> to select <guilabel>Error type</"
"guilabel>, choose the error column from the <guilabel>Data, +-</guilabel> "
"list. Format of the error bars can be defined using the <guilabel>Format:</"
"guilabel> pane."
msgstr ""
"Če želite narisati podatke s črtami napak, samo uvozite svoje podatke z "
"<link linkend=\"importdialog\">pogovornim oknom za uvoz</link> v svoj "
"projekt. Nato uporabite zavihek <guilabel>Vrstice napak</guilabel> v <link "
"linkend=\"properties-explorer\">lastnostih krivulje</link>, da izberete "
"<guilabel>Vrsto napake</guilabel>, izberite stolpec napake v "
"<guilabel>Podatki, +-</guilabel> seznam. Format vrstic napak lahko določite "
"s pomočjo podokna <guilabel>Format:</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1259
#, no-c-format
msgid "TeX label"
msgstr "Oznaka TeX"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For using TeX label you just have to activate the switch button "
"<guiicon>TeX</guiicon> in the <guilabel>Title</guilabel> tab. With that "
"every text you enter in the text box is rendered by TeX and plotted "
"accordingly. Since this conversion takes some time you may see a certain "
"delay when redrawing the plot."
msgstr ""
"Za uporabo oznake TeX morate samo aktivirati preklopni gumb <guiicon>TeX</"
"guiicon> v zavihku <guilabel>Naslov</guilabel>. S tem vsako besedilo, ki ga "
"vnesete v besedilno polje, upodobi TeX in ga ustrezno nariše. Ker ta "
"pretvorba traja nekaj časa, lahko opazite določeno zamudo pri ponovnem "
"risanju izrisa."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1275
#, no-c-format
msgid "Short Tutorials"
msgstr "Kratke vadnice"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1277
#, no-c-format
msgid "Building a sine graph with &LabPlot;"
msgstr "Gradnja sinusnega grafa z &LabPlot;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this chapter you will find explanations on how to build a simple plot for "
"a curve in the Cartesian coordinates from a mathematical equation."
msgstr ""
"V tem poglavju boste našli pojasnila o tem, kako iz matematične enačbe "
"zgraditi preprost izris krivulje v kartezičnih koordinatah."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1282 index.docbook:1456
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&LabPlot; window after the first start</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&LabPlot; okno po prvem zagonu</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1288 index.docbook:1462
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&LabPlot; window after the first start</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&LabPlot; okno po prvem zagonu</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1294 index.docbook:1468
