#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1649
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A time signal containing Morse code is Fourier transformed to frequency "
"space to see the main component. By applying a narrow band pass filter the "
"Morse signal is extracted and a nice ‘SOS’ can be seen:"
msgstr ""
"Časovni signal, ki vsebuje Morsejevo abecedo, se Fourier transformira v "
"frekvenčni prostor, da se vidi glavna komponenta. Z uporabo ozkopasovnega "
"filtra se izloči Morsejev signal in opaziti je mogoče lep \"SOS\":"

