#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1669
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Maxima session showing the chaotic dynamics of the Duffing oscillator. The "
"differential equation of the forced oscillator are solved with Maxima. Plots "
"of the trajectory, the phase space of the oscillator and the corresponding "
"Poincaré map are done with LabPlot:"
msgstr ""
"Seja Maxima, ki prikazuje kaotično dinamiko Duffingovega oscilatorja. "
"Diferencialna enačba prisilnega oscilatorja je rešena z Maxima. Izrisi "
"trajektorije, faznega prostora oscilatorja in ustrezne Poincaréjeve karte so "
"narejeni z LabPlot:"

