#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2270
#, no-c-format
msgid "Questions and Answers"
msgstr "Vprašanja in odgovori"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2276
#, no-c-format
msgid "For which platforms is &LabPlot; available?"
msgstr "Za katere platforme je &LabPlot; na voljo?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2279
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&LabPlot; is developed for Unix platforms and uses the &Qt; toolkit and &kde-"
"frameworks;. Normally you can expect &LabPlot; to build and run on every "
"platform &kde-frameworks; supports. A recent list of supported platforms and "
"tips for compiling and running &LabPlot; can be found on <ulink url=\"http://"
"labplot.wiki.sourceforge.net/Download\"> http://labplot.wiki.sourceforge.net/"
"Download</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&LabPlot; je razvit za platforme Unix in uporablja &Qt; komplet orodij in "
"&kde-frameworks;. Običajno lahko pričakujete &LabPlot; za izdelavo in "
"izvajanje na vsaki platformi &kde-frameworks; podpira. Nedavni seznam "
"podprtih platform in nasveti za prevajanje in izvajanje &LabPlot; najdete na "
"<ulink url=\"http://labplot.wiki.sourceforge.net/Download\"> http://labplot."
"wiki.sourceforge.net/Download</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2290
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I export the active worksheet as image?"
msgstr "Kako izvozim aktivni delovni list kot sliko?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The standard way is to use <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Export</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. All &Qt; supported "
"image formats are allowed. Just select the desired format and the active "
"worksheet is exported."
msgstr ""
"Standardni način je uporaba <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Izvoz</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Vsi &Qt; podprti "
"formati slik so dovoljeni. Samo izberite želeno obliko in aktivni delovni "
"list je izvožen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2299
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I use Greek letters for title, axes label, &etc;?"
msgstr "Kako uporabim grške črke za naslov, oznako osi, &etc;?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guiicon>&pi;</guiicon> button to open character selector window or "
"<guiicon>&tex;</guiicon> to generate Greek letters and other symbols using "
"&latex;."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite gumb <guiicon>&pi;</guiicon>, da odprete okno za izbiro znakov, "
"ali <guiicon>&tex;</guiicon>, da ustvarite grške črke in druge simbole z "
"&latex;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2310
#, no-c-format
msgid "I miss an important feature. What can I do?"
msgstr "Pogrešam pomembno lastnost. Kaj lahko naredim?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please take a look at the TODO file in the documentation of &LabPlot;. Here, "
"all planned features are listed in more or less sorted order which I will "
"implement in future releases of &LabPlot;. If you like to have additional "
"features or like to have a listed feature soon, mail me your wishes and, if "
"possible, send me example data or a short description of what you like to "
"do. It is not unlikely that your feature will appear in the next stable "
"release of &LabPlot; :-)"
msgstr ""
"Oglejte si datoteko TODO v dokumentaciji &LabPlot;. Tukaj so vse načrtovane "
"funkcije navedene v bolj ali manj razvrščenem vrstnem redu, ki jih bom "
"implementiral v prihodnjih izdajah &LabPlot;. Če želite imeti dodatne "
"funkcije ali želite kmalu imeti na seznamu funkcijo, mi pošljite svoje želje "
"in, če je mogoče, pošljite primer podatkov ali kratek opis tega, kar želite "
"početi. Ni malo verjetno, da se bo vaša funkcija pojavila v naslednji "
"stabilni izdaji &LabPlot; :-)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2328
#, no-c-format
msgid "Many Analysis functions are disabled. What can I do?"
msgstr "Številne funkcije analize so onemogočene. Kaj lahko naredim?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It looks like your &LabPlot; package was compiled without GSL (&GNU; "
"Scientific Library) support. &LabPlot; was designed to even work on systems "
"that are missing most of the standard libraries. Many distributions are "
"shipping &LabPlot; packages without this additional functionality. In this "
"case some functions are not available. Fortunately some programs (like "
"<application>pstoedit</application> or <application>texvc</application>) can "
"be added without recompiling &LabPlot;. You can always check your system "
"environment in the help menu of &LabPlot;."
msgstr ""
"Videti je, da vaš &LabPlot; paket je bil preveden brez podpore GSL (&GNU; "
"znanstvena knjižnica). &LabPlot; je bil zasnovan tako, da deluje tudi na "
"sistemih, ki nimajo večine standardnih knjižnic. Številne distribucije "
"pošiljajo &LabPlot; paketi brez te dodatne funkcije. V tem primeru nekatere "
"funkcije niso na voljo. Na srečo je mogoče nekatere programe (na primer "
"<application>pstoedit</application> ali <application>texvc</application>) "
"dodati brez ponovnega prevajanja &LabPlot;. Svoje sistemsko okolje lahko "
"vedno preverite v meniju za pomoč &LabPlot;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The packages provided on the official download page are always built with "
"the standard libraries (GSL, &etc;). You should use them to have all the "
"features."
msgstr ""
"Paketi, ki so na voljo na uradni strani za prenos, so vedno zgrajeni s "
"standardnimi knjižnicami (GSL itd.). Morate jih uporabiti, če želite imeti "
"vse funkcije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2342
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to help. How can I contribute to &LabPlot;?"
msgstr "Želim pomagati. Kako lahko prispevam k &LabPlot;?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2344
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes, of course. There are a lot things to do. Even if you don't know "
"anything about programming we always need people to find bugs, test things "
"and make suggestions. Also the translation and documentation always needs a "
"lot of work."
msgstr ""
"Seveda. Veliko je stvari za narediti. Tudi če ne veste ničesar o "
"programiranju, vedno potrebujemo ljudi, ki najdejo napake, testirajo stvari "
"in dajo predloge. Tudi prevod in dokumentacija zahtevata vedno veliko dela."

